details.name: Spirits
details.description: Summon five particle spirits that dance in a circle around Io. If a particle collides with an enemy hero, it explodes, damaging all enemy units in an area around it.  Creeps take minor damage from touching a particle spirit, but do not cause them to explode.  When its duration ends, any remaining Spirits explode. Upgradable by Aghanim's Scepter.
details.upgrade_description: Spirits now passively spawn around you constantly every second. Max of 5.
